# Welcome to your Mind pod 🎉

This is **your pod** — your own private space on the web for the things you make
and the data that’s yours. It belongs to you. You choose what to share and with
whom, and you can take it with you anytime.

## It’s yours
You own this pod, identified by <a href="{{webId}}">{{webId}}</a>.
Everything stored here is under your control.

## Build something
With [Mind Builder](http://localhost:3070/) you can wish for a website or app in
plain words and watch it get built — and everything it makes is saved right here,
in your pod.

## Have a look around
Want to peek at what’s inside? You can open your pod in the
[data browser](https://solidos.github.io/mashlib/dist/browse.html?uri={{base.path}}).

## Manage your account
To look after your pods, profile, and which apps can see your data,
[sign in to your account]({{oidcIssuer}}.account/).

## Learn more about Solid
Your pod runs on [Solid](https://solidproject.org/), an open standard for owning
your own data. The friendly folks on the [forum](https://forum.solidproject.org/)
are happy to help.
